text: Kam Wai Leung (born 6 July 1950) is a Hong Kong fencer. He competed in five events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Hong Kong male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Hong Kong Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Fencers at the 1974 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Hong Kong
